---
// About section - Editorial layout with red vertical line, 3 columns, and full-height image
---

<section class="about" id="nosotros">
  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-left">
      <div class="red-line"></div>
      <div class="about-text-area">
        <h2>SOBRE NOSOTROS</h2>

        <div class="about-columns">
          <div class="about-col">
            <span class="col-number">01</span>
            <h3 class="col-title">HISTORIA</h3>
            <p>Nacimos en 2026 con la visión de redefinir el streetwear argentino.</p>
            <p>Cada prenda refleja nuestra pasión por la cultura urbana y el diseño auténtico.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-col">
            <span class="col-number">02</span>
            <h3 class="col-title">FILOSOFÍA</h3>
            <p>Creemos que la moda es una extensión de la identidad personal.</p>
            <p>No seguimos tendencias efímeras: creamos piezas que trascienden temporadas.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-col">
            <span class="col-number">03</span>
            <h3 class="col-title">COMPROMISO</h3>
            <p>Materiales premium, producción consciente y atención obsesiva al detalle.</p>
            <p>Nuestro compromiso es con la calidad y quienes valoran el buen diseño.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1445205170230-053b83016050?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Melrose Atelier" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #000;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--borde);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-layout {
    display: flex;
    min-height: 600px;
  }

  .about-left {
    flex: 0 0 60%;
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    padding: 5rem 3rem 5rem 0;
  }

  .red-line {
    width: 4px;
    background: #c0392b;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-right: 3rem;
    margin-left: 3rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.4);
  }

  .about-text-area {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-text-area h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .col-number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: #c0392b;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .col-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--blanco);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-col p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--gris);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-image {
    flex: 0 0 40%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .about-image:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-left {
      flex: 0 0 55%;
      padding: 4rem 2rem 4rem 0;
    }

    .red-line {
      margin-left: 2rem;
      margin-right: 2rem;
    }

    .about-image {
      flex: 0 0 45%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-layout {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .about-left {
      flex: none;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .red-line {
      display: none;
    }

    .about-text-area h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .about-text-area h2::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #c0392b;
      margin: 1rem auto 0;
    }

    .about-columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-col {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      flex: none;
      height: 350px;
      z-index: 0;
    }
  }
</style>